Subject: [PATCH 066/120] firmware: rsu: add device attributes to sysfs
 interface

commit 930d68fad980a1f8c1287b6dc010329320b04447 from
https://github.com/altera-opensource/linux-socfpga.git

Add the following device attributes to Intel Stratix10 Remote System
Update (RSU) sysfs interface:
	dcmf0
	dcmf1
	dcmf2
	dcmf3
	max_retry

